            "TagType": 7,
            "TagName": "",
            "RawText": "*\n * The validation conditions are configured with an evaluation string when the validator is constructed. The string constructs an\n * Eval value that replaces any instance of the keyword \"value\" or \"val\" with the value being set. The result of the Eval\n * value evaluation is the output of the `validate` function call. For example, validators created with the string\n * \"value == 5\" would reject any value that is not equal to 5.\n",
            "ElementType": 2
          }
        ],
